# Batch scoring — one Redis round-trip for five transactions, verified.
Output demo/segments/segment8-batch.mp4
Output demo/segments/segment8-batch.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1500
Set Height 620
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Padding 18
Set Framerate 12

Hide
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Type "# Does /predict_batch really collapse the feature lookups?" Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "bash scripts/demo_batch.sh" Enter
Sleep 10s
